New Oreb Variables
| Variable                   | What it Measures                                                                        |
| -------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| expected_missed_fg         | Estimated number of missed field goals in the game                                      |
| expected_oreb_pressure     | Estimated pressure on the offensive glass based on missed shots and rebounding ability  |
| home_oreb_matchup          | Home team offensive rebounding ability relative to the away team’s defensive rebounding |
| away_oreb_matchup          | Away team offensive rebounding ability relative to the home team’s defensive rebounding |
| pace_rebound_pressure      | Interaction between game pace and rebound opportunities                                 |
| missed_fg_pg_diff          | Difference in missed field goals per game between teams                                 |
| orb_per100_diff            | Difference in offensive rebounds per 100 possessions                                    |
| drb_per100_diff            | Difference in defensive rebounds per 100 possessions                                    |
| trb_per100_dif             | Difference in total rebounds per 100 possessions                                        |
| last5_oreb_diff            | Difference in offensive rebounds over the last 5 games                                  |
| last10_oreb_diff           | Difference in offensive rebounds over the last 10 games                                 |
| last5_oreb_allowed_diff    | Difference in offensive rebounds allowed over the last 5 games                          |
| last10_oreb_allowed_diff   | Difference in offensive rebounds allowed over the last 10 games                         |



